        {
            "title": "舒淇同老公馮德倫係「老夫老妻」 冧爆指每日都係情人節  Rain預告8月到澳門開騷",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/42aaa2f46dcac9e05eb07c05b71a9ffe/2025-05/SQ.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/901b3c4f2b5171f0999b5014c1ca0102/207d155a32614d96a88e55cfedafa9e9-90930773ee01bb469aacc1d4994e68f4-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-681b880292132\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-681b880292134\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"舒淇同老公馮德倫係「老夫老妻」 冧爆指每日都係情人節  Rain預告8月到澳門開騷\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/bbe2f638436b51905cb97cb52f898d53/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250507/_2025050722405221855.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">舒淇同老公馮德倫係「老夫老妻」 冧爆指每日都係情人節  Rain預告8月到澳門開騷</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>舒淇到澳門出席活動，問到上月生日有否和老公馮德倫出去玩，她指最近比較忙沒時間去玩，問可會補祝生日，她甜笑指每日都是情人節，也有和老公吃飯慶祝。她表示難得來澳門，也想四出去品嘗道地美食，也想去看摩天輪，覺得澳門好繁華，非常適合娛樂和看表演，是夢幻的城市。問想和老公同遊澳門嗎？她笑言：「我們老夫老妻啦！」\n\n</p><h2> Rain趕回韓國拍拳擊新劇</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"問到上月生日有否和老公馮德倫出去玩，舒淇指最近比較忙沒時間去玩。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/00b373d0271581a94f549a259929ddc9/2025-05/_DSC4776.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        問到上月生日有否和老公馮德倫出去玩，舒淇指最近比較忙沒時間去玩。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"舒淇冧爆指同老公馮德倫係「老夫老妻」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f67e8955fd12c9b3cd58e5b7d5fa599b/2025-05/_DSC4771.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        舒淇冧爆指同老公馮德倫係「老夫老妻」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"韓國男神Rain表示首次來澳門欣賞水舞間。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8c5e32816da64e3b164478a9073a2244/2025-05/_DSC4715.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        韓國男神Rain表示首次來澳門欣賞水舞間。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Rain活動後就要趕回韓國，繼續拍攝新劇，透露題材與拳擊有關。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4bf811611152a02d79e17d8310bf50bd/2025-05/_DSC4725.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Rain活動後就要趕回韓國，繼續拍攝新劇，透露題材與拳擊有關。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Rain透露新劇有很多動作場面。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b26efd65b3a897c1775ab1a472ad2ff1/2025-05/_DSC4703.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Rain透露新劇有很多動作場面。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Rain又說8月會到澳門開騷，粉絲一定好開心。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4d8b0fcf41aeeac9d908366fa95cffcd/2025-05/_DSC4705.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Rain又說8月會到澳門開騷，粉絲一定好開心。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Kelly亦有到澳門出席活動。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/914eab3bdbbdd9355d5893d9b3db5bcb/2025-05/_DSC4555.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Kelly亦有到澳門出席活動。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Kelly好高貴啊！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/944c528f6ea611e1a4d3b65f90425cfe/2025-05/_DSC4591.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Kelly好高貴啊！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<p>韓國男神Rain表示首次來澳門欣賞水舞間，興奮又期待，不過活動後就要趕回韓國，繼續拍攝新劇，透露將於年尾播映，題材與拳擊有關，所以有很多動作場面，又說8月會到澳門開騷，有機會會再來開騷。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
